title: The Complete Guide to Digital Painting Vol 3 - 2010  UK
description:
The Complete Guide to Digital Painting Vol 3 - 2010  UK

260 Pages | True PDF | English | 49 MB 


Whether you have been painting digitally for years or just getting started, this book is your guide to Corel's Painter software. Packed full with expert tips and advice, step-by-step workshops and inspirational imagery, this guide will transform your artworks today! Paint amazing artwork today from photo or from a sketch and build up impressive digital paintings with our expert tips and tricks and re-create famous works of art by learning how you can emulate the most famous art styles of all time with our Paint Like series.
